comment: Lemma for ~ hsmex . Bound the order type of a union of sets of ordinals, each of limited order type. Vaguely reminiscent of ~ unictb but use of order types allows to canonically choose the sub-bijections, removing the choice requirement. (Contributed by Stefan O'Rear, 14-Feb-2015.)
